ader-background:none; --hawk-footer-game-platform-border:solid 1px var(--game-platform-grey); --site-logo-width:100%; --site-logo-max-width:none; --hawk-tab-text-color:#666; --hawk-tab-background:#d6d6d6; --review-rows-background:var(--white); --seasonal-event-grey:#797979; --seasonal-event-dark-grey:#313131; --price-widget-padding:none; --price-widget-border-bottom:none; --postcode-entry-button-color:var(--site-color); --was-price-text-color:#848484; --was-price-promo-color:#be0707; --was-price-light-promo-color:#ededed; --was-price-light-promo-text-color:#be0707; --dotw-header-border-top:1px solid #ddd; --dotw-header-border-bottom:4px solid #006ea9; --dotw-toggle-background-color:#1b1b1b; --dotw-search-input-border-color:#ddd; --dotw-header-background:transparent; --dotw-header-text-color:var(--black); --shopping-partners-header-background-color:#f26722; --hover-panel-color:orange; --tv-channels-display-label-color:#696969; --user-input-color:#c1c1c1; --user-input-hover-color:#535353; --user-input-input-background:#f2f2f2; --user-input-input-error-color:#838383; --radio-button-color:#c1c1c1; --checkbox-color:#c1c1c1; --range-filter-shadow-color:#a9a9a9; --range-filter-background-color:var(--site-color); --index-color:#999; --comparison-load-more-background-color:#262626; --pre-order-promise-color:#aaa; --description-hover-background:#cac7c7; --display-price-code-color:var(--site-color); --merchant-link-mona-background-color:var(--site-color); --merchant-link-mona-text-color: inherit; --mona-site-font-family: inherit; --shop-filter-button-background-color:var(--trd-blue); --shop-filter-button-text-color:var(--white); --pagination-button-selected-background-color:var(--trd-blue); --deal-widget-border-color:#ddd; --deal-hero-promo-background:#e6248a; --deal-hero-promo-color:#fff; --deal-hero-promo-background-progressive:transparent; --deal-hero-promo-color-progressive:#d21f26; --site-color:#f26722; --heading-color:linear-gradient(#3c4249,#232128); --tab-color:var(--site-color); --toggle-color:var(--site-color); --toggle-switch-color:var(--site-color); --editors-pick-promo-color:var(--site-color); --editors-pick-promo-rgba-color:rgba(242,103,34,0.3); --model-options-filter-color:var(--site-color); --countdown-in-progress-color:var(--site-color); --rows-background-color:transparent; --mpu-header-height:25px; --mpu-header-padding:5px 0; --review-background:transparent; --review-peacock-background:#ededed; --product-label-background:var(--grey); --product-label-text-color:var(--white); --seasonal-event-merchants-background:transparent; --game-platform-background:#ededed; --hawk-footer-background:transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\"></aside><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 596.99px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\">Beyond Light delves deep into mortality, the nature of the Darkness, the questionable righteousness of Guardians, and the humanity of enemies like the Fallen in a way that previous expansions never dared to, or really even could have. After all, it\'s hard to distinguish between the Fallen trying to kill you and the Fallen who might understandably be fleeing a tyrannical despot when the only direction you have is to kill dudes and the main feedback you receive is, \"Great job killing those dudes.\" This story is much more nuanced and creative.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 596.99px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\">Sometimes your Ghost questions your actions, other times the Vanguard leaders criticize your methods, and there\'s a clear divide underpinning it all which I hope comes to a head in future expansions. I want characters to leave and die and betray and surprise, and for the first time in a long time, it feels like Destiny 2 might actually pull some of that off. The best characterization comes late in the campaign as you get to know the Exo Stranger and her past, which has quickly become one of my favorite stories in the Destiny universe – one that not only ties up loose threads from the first game, but also builds on one of the most interesting characters in the lore, Clovis Bray.&nbsp;</p><div id=\"ad-unit-2\" class=\"ad-unit\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\"></div><div class=\"slot-double-height-2-336\" data-feat-ref=\"bordeaux-feat-id-49\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237); position: relative; display: flex; flex: 1 1 0%; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; height: 0px;\"></div><div class=\"slot-double-height-image-1\" data-feat-ref=\"bordeaux-feat-id-50\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; co