" lazy-image-van optional-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-970-80.jpg 970w\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-970-80.jpg 970w\" data-was-processed=\"true\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><img src=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" alt=\"Destiny 2 Beyond Light review in progress\" class=\"lazy-image-van optional-image loaded\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-970-80.jpg 970w\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e.jpg\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zkdB3fVnusQHPQGrf6Mf9e-970-80.jpg 970w\" data-was-processed=\"true\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; top: 0px; left: 0px; position: absolute; height: 335.803px; width: 596.99px; background-color: unset;\"></picture></p></div><figcaption itemprop=\"caption description\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 16px; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline-block; width: 596.99px;\"><span class=\"credit\" itemprop=\"copyrightHolder\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 16px; font-size: 12px; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; display: inline-block;\">(Image credit: Bungie)</span></figcaption></figure><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 596.99px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\">A new subclass is just a nice surprise, but any Destiny 2 expansion is truly tested by the variety and quality of its loot, and here too Beyond Light is a bit off-kilter. It\'s introduced some of the best and most inventive weapon perks yet, but its loot pool is disappointingly small for an expansion. A recent update helped offset this by bringing back a bunch of old guns, and the new raid guns are extremely desirable, but with only two dozen truly new weapons available, Beyond Light definitely feels a bit samey. There\'s still no special Strike loot, we\'re&nbsp;<em style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">still&nbsp;</em>waiting on an increasingly necessary vendor refresh, and many weapon archetypes have gone desperately underserved.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 596.99px; height: auto; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\">The good news is that when we do get new weapons – and we will – they\'re bound to kick ass thanks to all these awesome new perks. Gone are the days of \"reload perk and damage perk.\" We\'re in an ability economy now, baby. Thresh and Wellspring refuel your abilities on kills, Surplus can turn any clunker into a lightweight killing machine, and the return of unique raid perks (!) has given endgame loot some much-needed bite. The loot pool may be small, but there are nearly a dozen weapons that I want to grind for, and I\'m looking forward to that grind.&nbsp;</p><div class=\"slot-double-height-image-3\" data-feat-ref=\"bordeaux-feat-id-55\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237); position: relative; display: flex; flex: 1 1 0%; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; height: 0px;\"></div><figure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(237, 237, 237);\"><div class=\"image-widthsetter\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 596.99px; max-width: 2559px;\"><p class=\"vanilla-image-block\" style=\"font-family: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 317.476px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 0; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; height: 0px; width: 596.99px;\"><picture style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><source type=\"image/webp\" alt=\"Destiny 2 Lament\" class=\" lazy-image-van optional-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-970-80.jpg.webp 970w\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-320-80.jpg.webp 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-650-80.jpg.webp 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-970-80.jpg.webp 970w\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><source type=\"image/jpeg\" alt=\"Destiny 2 Lament\" class=\" lazy-image-van optional-image\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1000px) 970px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-normal=\"https://vanilla.futurecdn.net/gamesradar/media/img/missing-image.svg\" data-srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-970-80.jpg 970w\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-320-80.jpg 320w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-650-80.jpg 650w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/wg2DuA22tM3NgUknVzLGTo-970-80.jpg 970w\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"></picture></p></div></figure>', '2020-12-24', 'llkkoaio');
INSERT INTO `games` (`id`, `name`, `rate`, `imagepath`, `author`, `post`, `date`, `itchio_link`) VALUES
(63, 'Game 100', 8, 'http://localhost:8001/uploads/g3-1607043714520.jpg', 'Elie Azar', '<div class=\"c-entry-content \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; position: relative;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In 2018, Tetris Effect\'s mesmerizing sounds and sights heightened the classic game\'s aesthetically pleasing properties and its ability to consume our attention to almost therapeutic levels, reinvigorating our appreciation for one of gaming\'s oldest obsessions. But even as former GameSpot editor Peter Brown proclaimed Tetris \"<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tetris-effect-review-better-than-ever/1900-6417033/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\"><ins style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\">better than ever</ins></a>\" in Tetris Effect, he noted it \"sadly\" did not apply its wondrous approach to multiplayer. Two years later,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/games/tetris-effect-connected/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-516157\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\">Tetris Effect: Connected</a>--an updated re-release for Xbox consoles and PC--fills that gap. Just as the original did for the classic version of the game, Connected reimagines Tetris multiplayer with flair and vision. It also loses a major component, VR support, which delivers the most intense version of the experience. While I\'m of two minds on that tradeoff, the soothing intensity of Tetris Effect hasn\'t lost any potency. On the contrary, it feels more vital than ever in 2020.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Though it adds and removes modes whole cloth, the core of Tetris Effect remains unchanged. Despite the fact that Journey mode hasn\'t been touched, its shifting, syncopated themes enraptured me level by level, even on my second time through. Tetris Effect is a significant challenge to average Tetris players like myself. Each level revs the speed up to push you just up to the edge of what you can handle. Even as you improve--and you are getting better, whether you see it or not--the levels scale to demand your full focus. It sounds unapproachable, but there\'s something about the combination of the way your brain looks for patterns, combined with the rhythmic sensory elements and this challenge, that lets you give yourself over to the game, almost trance-like, without even trying.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You\'ll need that focus in multiplayer. Whether you\'re playing cooperatively with other players or competing against them, the multiplayer modes in Connected ratchet up the intensity found in the original. Connected features four multiplayer modes--three competitive, one co-op. As in most games, other players will push you in ways a single-player campaign will not.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Most players will rush right to Zone Battle, an updated version of what I imagine when I think of competitive Tetris, a survival mode where completing lines on your field creates extra garbage lines for your opponents. The Connected version adds the zone mechanic from Tetris Effect, which stops the parade of pieces and allows you to complete a large number of lines in a short time. Using zone effectively adds an extra layer of strategy: Activating it at the right time can guarantee a victory, but it\'s surprisingly tricky to find the correct moment to use it. Though it seems like the ability to save up and cash in lines would only intensify the dominance of elite players, I found it allowed you to turn a good flow into a meaningful attack, regardless of whether you\'re winning or losing. It won\'t keep a superior player from stomping you, mind you, but zone rewards players who can be mindful of the situations on both fields and retain the focus to clear lines.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition to Zone Battle, Connected also has two versions of Score Attack, a more traditional competitive mode without garbage-line or zone mechanics. In standard Score Attack, you play for the high score and survival. In Classic Score Attack, you do the same, but with the original 1984 rules, so you can\'t bank pieces, use T-Spins, and so on.</p><div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart incontent-leader-loaded\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; visibility: visible; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 1.3rem -100px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad skybox-inContent\" id=\"incontent-ad\" data-ad=\"incontent-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMTImJOQs-0CFQfUGwodgTINow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; max-width: none; border: 0pt none; margin: 0px auto !important;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-google-container-id=\"4\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; max-width: none; display: block; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px auto !important;\"></iframe></div></div></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zone Battle is an interesting riff, but it\'s a known quantity. The most interesting mode--this game\'s crown jewel--is the eponymous Connected co-op mode, where three players collectively try to outlast a series of AI opponents, one at a time. At first, the four players simply play Tetris. The AI enemies, named after the signs of the Zodiac, have special abilities called “blitzes” to make things difficult for you, which range from annoying parlor tricks like moving your field up and down to genuinely infuriating maneuvers like temporarily increasing the speed of your drops to force errors. Once a week, there\'s also an asynchronous Connected Versus mode, where players can spar 3-on-1.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When the three human players clear enough lines on their fields, you automatically trigger a special form of the zone ability, which combines all three of your fields into one. You and your partners take turns placing pieces on the extra-wide field and must clear extra-long lines. Like every level and mode in Tetris Effect, you need to find a natural rhythm in the game, but in this case you do so by getting in sync with your partners. Only one person plays a piece at a time, so being able to quickly find the right spot and anticipate where the others will go becomes crucial. Like zone battle, you need to be focused to fill gaps quickly, but also mindful of the whole field and what\'s happening.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><figure data-embed-type=\"gallery\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220,1300-3767221,1300-3767222,1300-3767223,1300-3767224,1300-3767226,1300-3767227,1300-3767228\" data-resize-urls=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 1rem 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: bold; position: relative; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"image-gallery__label\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(216, 216, 216);\">Gallery</div><div class=\"image-gallery__list hide-scrollbar \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; position: relative; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; display: grid; justify-content: space-between; grid-auto-flow: column; overflow-x: auto;\"><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 1\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767221\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 2\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767222\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 3\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767223\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 4\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767224\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 5\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a></div></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most games, that kind of coordination would require voice chat, but this particular mode benefits from relying on non-verbal communication. It requires more awareness and consideration of your fellow players than the competitive modes because you\'re sharing a single field. The goal of Tetris Effect, across its modes, is to feel the flow of the game without interruption or getting into your own head; silently syncing with your partners, showing them what you plan to do with your next piece and trusting that they\'ll understand and plan around that offers an interesting variation on that theme, and it can create incredible results if you can... connect.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Since it\'s a re-release, we should also talk about what\'s missing from Connected. Unlike the original release, Tetris Effect isn\'t playable in virtual reality. Since Connected is primarily an Xbox release, removing VR seems like a practical decision: The Xbox consoles don\'t support VR headsets, so only PC players would be able to enjoy it. In the original Tetris Effect, VR felt like the coup de gras, tuning you into the game intensely by letting you see and hear the levels all around you. It\'s a unique experience, and part of the magic of the original version. While I think multiplayer is the more approachable feature, and what I would want if forced to choose, I do wish there were a way to have both in a single package.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But there\'s no time for regrets in Tetris. The next piece is falling and you only have a few seconds to put it in place. Then the next piece, and the one after that. Some people meditate to clear their minds. Other people cook, or build models. Tetris Effect has a similar capacity to clear your mind. In 2018, that made Tetris Effect feel special. In 2020, it feels essential.</p></div><div data-concert-ads-name=\"connatix-feature-desktop\" class=\"connatix-feature-desktop\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 32px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 730px;\"><div id=\"connatix-feature-desktop\" class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><div class=\"player-cnx-div\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; min-height: 10px; height: 410.621px;\"><cnx class=\"cnx-main-container cnx-in-desktop cnx-el cnx-main-container-flex\" style=\"box-sizing: content-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: 1; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); width: 729.999px; height: auto; position: relative; overflow: hidden; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); max-width: 800px; display: flex !important;\"><div class=\"cnx-resize-triggers\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; animation: 1ms ease 0s 1 normal none running resizeanim; visibility: hidden; opacity: 0; content: &quot; &quot;; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; height: 410.621px; width: 729.999px; overflow: hidden;\"><div class=\"cnx-expand-trigger\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; content: &quot; &quot;; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; height: 410.621px; width: 729.999px; overflow: auto; background: rgb(238, 238, 238); color: rgb(66, 66, 66);\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration: inherit; vertical-align: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 731px; height: 412px;\"></div></div></div></cnx></div></div></div>', '2020-12-01', 'sssss');
INSERT INTO `games` (`id`, `name`, `rate`, `imagepath`, `author`, `post`, `date`, `itchio_link`) VALUES
(64, 'Game 101', 7, 'http://localhost:8001/uploads/g4-1607043748025.jpg', 'John', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In 2018, Tetris Effect\'s mesmerizing sounds and sights heightened the classic game\'s aesthetically pleasing properties and its ability to consume our attention to almost therapeutic levels, reinvigorating our appreciation for one of gaming\'s oldest obsessions. But even as former GameSpot editor Peter Brown proclaimed Tetris \"<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tetris-effect-review-better-than-ever/1900-6417033/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\"><ins style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\">better than ever</ins></a>\" in Tetris Effect, he noted it \"sadly\" did not apply its wondrous approach to multiplayer. Two years later,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/games/tetris-effect-connected/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-516157\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\">Tetris Effect: Connected</a>--an updated re-release for Xbox consoles and PC--fills that gap. Just as the original did for the classic version of the game, Connected reimagines Tetris multiplayer with flair and vision. It also loses a major component, VR support, which delivers the most intense version of the experience. While I\'m of two minds on that tradeoff, the soothing intensity of Tetris Effect hasn\'t lost any potency. On the contrary, it feels more vital than ever in 2020.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Though it adds and removes modes whole cloth, the core of Tetris Effect remains unchanged. Despite the fact that Journey mode hasn\'t been touched, its shifting, syncopated themes enraptured me level by level, even on my second time through. Tetris Effect is a significant challenge to average Tetris players like myself. Each level revs the speed up to push you just up to the edge of what you can handle. Even as you improve--and you are getting better, whether you see it or not--the levels scale to demand your full focus. It sounds unapproachable, but there\'s something about the combination of the way your brain looks for patterns, combined with the rhythmic sensory elements and this challenge, that lets you give yourself over to the game, almost trance-like, without even trying.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You\'ll need that focus in multiplayer. Whether you\'re playing cooperatively with other players or competing against them, the multiplayer modes in Connected ratchet up the intensity found in the original. Connected features four multiplayer modes--three competitive, one co-op. As in most games, other players will push you in ways a single-player campaign will not.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Most players will rush right to Zone Battle, an updated version of what I imagine when I think of competitive Tetris, a survival mode where completing lines on your field creates extra garbage lines for your opponents. The Connected version adds the zone mechanic from Tetris Effect, which stops the parade of pieces and allows you to complete a large number of lines in a short time. Using zone effectively adds an extra layer of strategy: Activating it at the right time can guarantee a victory, but it\'s surprisingly tricky to find the correct moment to use it. Though it seems like the ability to save up and cash in lines would only intensify the dominance of elite players, I found it allowed you to turn a good flow into a meaningful attack, regardless of whether you\'re winning or losing. It won\'t keep a superior player from stomping you, mind you, but zone rewards players who can be mindful of the situations on both fields and retain the focus to clear lines.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition to Zone Battle, Connected also has two versions of Score Attack, a more traditional competitive mode without garbage-line or zone mechanics. In standard Score Attack, you play for the high score and survival. In Classic Score Attack, you do the same, but with the original 1984 rules, so you can\'t bank pieces, use T-Spins, and so on.</p><div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart incontent-leader-loaded\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; visibility: visible; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 1.3rem -100px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad skybox-inContent\" id=\"incontent-ad\" data-ad=\"incontent-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMTImJOQs-0CFQfUGwodgTINow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; max-width: none; border: 0pt none; margin: 0px auto !important;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-google-container-id=\"4\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; max-width: none; display: block; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px auto !important;\"></iframe></div></div></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zone Battle is an interesting riff, but it\'s a known quantity. The most interesting mode--this game\'s crown jewel--is the eponymous Connected co-op mode, where three players collectively try to outlast a series of AI opponents, one at a time. At first, the four players simply play Tetris. The AI enemies, named after the signs of the Zodiac, have special abilities called “blitzes” to make things difficult for you, which range from annoying parlor tricks like moving your field up and down to genuinely infuriating maneuvers like temporarily increasing the speed of your drops to force errors. Once a week, there\'s also an asynchronous Connected Versus mode, where players can spar 3-on-1.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When the three human players clear enough lines on their fields, you automatically trigger a special form of the zone ability, which combines all three of your fields into one. You and your partners take turns placing pieces on the extra-wide field and must clear extra-long lines. Like every level and mode in Tetris Effect, you need to find a natural rhythm in the game, but in this case you do so by getting in sync with your partners. Only one person plays a piece at a time, so being able to quickly find the right spot and anticipate where the others will go becomes crucial. Like zone battle, you need to be focused to fill gaps quickly, but also mindful of the whole field and what\'s happening.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><figure data-embed-type=\"gallery\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220,1300-3767221,1300-3767222,1300-3767223,1300-3767224,1300-3767226,1300-3767227,1300-3767228\" data-resize-urls=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 1rem 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: bold; position: relative; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"image-gallery__label\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(216, 216, 216);\">Gallery</div><div class=\"image-gallery__list hide-scrollbar \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; position: relative; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; display: grid; justify-content: space-between; grid-auto-flow: column; overflow-x: auto;\"><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 1\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767221\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 2\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767222\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 3\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767223\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 4\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767224\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 5\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a></div></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most games, that kind of coordination would require voice chat, but this particular mode benefits from relying on non-verbal communication. It requires more awareness and consideration of your fellow players than the competitive modes because you\'re sharing a single field. The goal of Tetris Effect, across its modes, is to feel the flow of the game without interruption or getting into your own head; silently syncing with your partners, showing them what you plan to do with your next piece and trusting that they\'ll understand and plan around that offers an interesting variation on that theme, and it can create incredible results if you can... connect.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Since it\'s a re-release, we should also talk about what\'s missing from Connected. Unlike the original release, Tetris Effect isn\'t playable in virtual reality. Since Connected is primarily an Xbox release, removing VR seems like a practical decision: The Xbox consoles don\'t support VR headsets, so only PC players would be able to enjoy it. In the original Tetris Effect, VR felt like the coup de gras, tuning you into the game intensely by letting you see and hear the levels all around you. It\'s a unique experience, and part of the magic of the original version. While I think multiplayer is the more approachable feature, and what I would want if forced to choose, I do wish there were a way to have both in a single package.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But there\'s no time for regrets in Tetris. The next piece is falling and you only have a few seconds to put it in place. Then the next piece, and the one after that. Some people meditate to clear their minds. Other people cook, or build models. Tetris Effect has a similar capacity to clear your mind. In 2018, that made Tetris Effect feel special. In 2020, it feels essential.</p>', '2020-12-24', 'sss');
INSERT INTO `games` (`id`, `name`, `rate`, `imagepath`, `author`, `post`, `date`, `itchio_link`) VALUES
(65, 'Game 102', 7, 'http://localhost:8001/uploads/g5-1607043780858.jpg', 'Khaldoun', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In 2018, Tetris Effect\'s mesmerizing sounds and sights heightened the classic game\'s aesthetically pleasing properties and its ability to consume our attention to almost therapeutic levels, reinvigorating our appreciation for one of gaming\'s oldest obsessions. But even as former GameSpot editor Peter Brown proclaimed Tetris \"<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tetris-effect-review-better-than-ever/1900-6417033/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\"><ins style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\">better than ever</ins></a>\" in Tetris Effect, he noted it \"sadly\" did not apply its wondrous approach to multiplayer. Two years later,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/games/tetris-effect-connected/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-516157\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\">Tetris Effect: Connected</a>--an updated re-release for Xbox consoles and PC--fills that gap. Just as the original did for the classic version of the game, Connected reimagines Tetris multiplayer with flair and vision. It also loses a major component, VR support, which delivers the most intense version of the experience. While I\'m of two minds on that tradeoff, the soothing intensity of Tetris Effect hasn\'t lost any potency. On the contrary, it feels more vital than ever in 2020.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Though it adds and removes modes whole cloth, the core of Tetris Effect remains unchanged. Despite the fact that Journey mode hasn\'t been touched, its shifting, syncopated themes enraptured me level by level, even on my second time through. Tetris Effect is a significant challenge to average Tetris players like myself. Each level revs the speed up to push you just up to the edge of what you can handle. Even as you improve--and you are getting better, whether you see it or not--the levels scale to demand your full focus. It sounds unapproachable, but there\'s something about the combination of the way your brain looks for patterns, combined with the rhythmic sensory elements and this challenge, that lets you give yourself over to the game, almost trance-like, without even trying.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You\'ll need that focus in multiplayer. Whether you\'re playing cooperatively with other players or competing against them, the multiplayer modes in Connected ratchet up the intensity found in the original. Connected features four multiplayer modes--three competitive, one co-op. As in most games, other players will push you in ways a single-player campaign will not.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Most players will rush right to Zone Battle, an updated version of what I imagine when I think of competitive Tetris, a survival mode where completing lines on your field creates extra garbage lines for your opponents. The Connected version adds the zone mechanic from Tetris Effect, which stops the parade of pieces and allows you to complete a large number of lines in a short time. Using zone effectively adds an extra layer of strategy: Activating it at the right time can guarantee a victory, but it\'s surprisingly tricky to find the correct moment to use it. Though it seems like the ability to save up and cash in lines would only intensify the dominance of elite players, I found it allowed you to turn a good flow into a meaningful attack, regardless of whether you\'re winning or losing. It won\'t keep a superior player from stomping you, mind you, but zone rewards players who can be mindful of the situations on both fields and retain the focus to clear lines.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition to Zone Battle, Connected also has two versions of Score Attack, a more traditional competitive mode without garbage-line or zone mechanics. In standard Score Attack, you play for the high score and survival. In Classic Score Attack, you do the same, but with the original 1984 rules, so you can\'t bank pieces, use T-Spins, and so on.</p><div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart incontent-leader-loaded\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; visibility: visible; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 1.3rem -100px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad skybox-inContent\" id=\"incontent-ad\" data-ad=\"incontent-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMTImJOQs-0CFQfUGwodgTINow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; max-width: none; border: 0pt none; margin: 0px auto !important;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-google-container-id=\"4\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; max-width: none; display: block; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px auto !important;\"></iframe></div></div></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zone Battle is an interesting riff, but it\'s a known quantity. The most interesting mode--this game\'s crown jewel--is the eponymous Connected co-op mode, where three players collectively try to outlast a series of AI opponents, one at a time. At first, the four players simply play Tetris. The AI enemies, named after the signs of the Zodiac, have special abilities called “blitzes” to make things difficult for you, which range from annoying parlor tricks like moving your field up and down to genuinely infuriating maneuvers like temporarily increasing the speed of your drops to force errors. Once a week, there\'s also an asynchronous Connected Versus mode, where players can spar 3-on-1.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When the three human players clear enough lines on their fields, you automatically trigger a special form of the zone ability, which combines all three of your fields into one. You and your partners take turns placing pieces on the extra-wide field and must clear extra-long lines. Like every level and mode in Tetris Effect, you need to find a natural rhythm in the game, but in this case you do so by getting in sync with your partners. Only one person plays a piece at a time, so being able to quickly find the right spot and anticipate where the others will go becomes crucial. Like zone battle, you need to be focused to fill gaps quickly, but also mindful of the whole field and what\'s happening.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><figure data-embed-type=\"gallery\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220,1300-3767221,1300-3767222,1300-3767223,1300-3767224,1300-3767226,1300-3767227,1300-3767228\" data-resize-urls=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 1rem 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: bold; position: relative; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"image-gallery__label\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(216, 216, 216);\">Gallery</div><div class=\"image-gallery__list hide-scrollbar \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; position: relative; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; display: grid; justify-content: space-between; grid-auto-flow: column; overflow-x: auto;\"><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 1\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767221\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 2\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767222\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 3\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767223\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 4\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767224\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 5\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a></div></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most games, that kind of coordination would require voice chat, but this particular mode benefits from relying on non-verbal communication. It requires more awareness and consideration of your fellow players than the competitive modes because you\'re sharing a single field. The goal of Tetris Effect, across its modes, is to feel the flow of the game without interruption or getting into your own head; silently syncing with your partners, showing them what you plan to do with your next piece and trusting that they\'ll understand and plan around that offers an interesting variation on that theme, and it can create incredible results if you can... connect.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Since it\'s a re-release, we should also talk about what\'s missing from Connected. Unlike the original release, Tetris Effect isn\'t playable in virtual reality. Since Connected is primarily an Xbox release, removing VR seems like a practical decision: The Xbox consoles don\'t support VR headsets, so only PC players would be able to enjoy it. In the original Tetris Effect, VR felt like the coup de gras, tuning you into the game intensely by letting you see and hear the levels all around you. It\'s a unique experience, and part of the magic of the original version. While I think multiplayer is the more approachable feature, and what I would want if forced to choose, I do wish there were a way to have both in a single package.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But there\'s no time for regrets in Tetris. The next piece is falling and you only have a few seconds to put it in place. Then the next piece, and the one after that. Some people meditate to clear their minds. Other people cook, or build models. Tetris Effect has a similar capacity to clear your mind. In 2018, that made Tetris Effect feel special. In 2020, it feels essential.</p>', '2020-12-01', 'mm');
INSERT INTO `games` (`id`, `name`, `rate`, `imagepath`, `author`, `post`, `date`, `itchio_link`) VALUES
(66, 'Game 103', 9, 'http://localhost:8001/uploads/g7-1607043808518.jpg', 'Samar', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In 2018, Tetris Effect\'s mesmerizing sounds and sights heightened the classic game\'s aesthetically pleasing properties and its ability to consume our attention to almost therapeutic levels, reinvigorating our appreciation for one of gaming\'s oldest obsessions. But even as former GameSpot editor Peter Brown proclaimed Tetris \"<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tetris-effect-review-better-than-ever/1900-6417033/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\"><ins style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\">better than ever</ins></a>\" in Tetris Effect, he noted it \"sadly\" did not apply its wondrous approach to multiplayer. Two years later,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/games/tetris-effect-connected/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-516157\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\">Tetris Effect: Connected</a>--an updated re-release for Xbox consoles and PC--fills that gap. Just as the original did for the classic version of the game, Connected reimagines Tetris multiplayer with flair and vision. It also loses a major component, VR support, which delivers the most intense version of the experience. While I\'m of two minds on that tradeoff, the soothing intensity of Tetris Effect hasn\'t lost any potency. On the contrary, it feels more vital than ever in 2020.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Though it adds and removes modes whole cloth, the core of Tetris Effect remains unchanged. Despite the fact that Journey mode hasn\'t been touched, its shifting, syncopated themes enraptured me level by level, even on my second time through. Tetris Effect is a significant challenge to average Tetris players like myself. Each level revs the speed up to push you just up to the edge of what you can handle. Even as you improve--and you are getting better, whether you see it or not--the levels scale to demand your full focus. It sounds unapproachable, but there\'s something about the combination of the way your brain looks for patterns, combined with the rhythmic sensory elements and this challenge, that lets you give yourself over to the game, almost trance-like, without even trying.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You\'ll need that focus in multiplayer. Whether you\'re playing cooperatively with other players or competing against them, the multiplayer modes in Connected ratchet up the intensity found in the original. Connected features four multiplayer modes--three competitive, one co-op. As in most games, other players will push you in ways a single-player campaign will not.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Most players will rush right to Zone Battle, an updated version of what I imagine when I think of competitive Tetris, a survival mode where completing lines on your field creates extra garbage lines for your opponents. The Connected version adds the zone mechanic from Tetris Effect, which stops the parade of pieces and allows you to complete a large number of lines in a short time. Using zone effectively adds an extra layer of strategy: Activating it at the right time can guarantee a victory, but it\'s surprisingly tricky to find the correct moment to use it. Though it seems like the ability to save up and cash in lines would only intensify the dominance of elite players, I found it allowed you to turn a good flow into a meaningful attack, regardless of whether you\'re winning or losing. It won\'t keep a superior player from stomping you, mind you, but zone rewards players who can be mindful of the situations on both fields and retain the focus to clear lines.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition to Zone Battle, Connected also has two versions of Score Attack, a more traditional competitive mode without garbage-line or zone mechanics. In standard Score Attack, you play for the high score and survival. In Classic Score Attack, you do the same, but with the original 1984 rules, so you can\'t bank pieces, use T-Spins, and so on.</p><div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart incontent-leader-loaded\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; visibility: visible; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 1.3rem -100px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad skybox-inContent\" id=\"incontent-ad\" data-ad=\"incontent-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMTImJOQs-0CFQfUGwodgTINow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; max-width: none; border: 0pt none; margin: 0px auto !important;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-google-container-id=\"4\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; max-width: none; display: block; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px auto !important;\"></iframe></div></div></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zone Battle is an interesting riff, but it\'s a known quantity. The most interesting mode--this game\'s crown jewel--is the eponymous Connected co-op mode, where three players collectively try to outlast a series of AI opponents, one at a time. At first, the four players simply play Tetris. The AI enemies, named after the signs of the Zodiac, have special abilities called “blitzes” to make things difficult for you, which range from annoying parlor tricks like moving your field up and down to genuinely infuriating maneuvers like temporarily increasing the speed of your drops to force errors. Once a week, there\'s also an asynchronous Connected Versus mode, where players can spar 3-on-1.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When the three human players clear enough lines on their fields, you automatically trigger a special form of the zone ability, which combines all three of your fields into one. You and your partners take turns placing pieces on the extra-wide field and must clear extra-long lines. Like every level and mode in Tetris Effect, you need to find a natural rhythm in the game, but in this case you do so by getting in sync with your partners. Only one person plays a piece at a time, so being able to quickly find the right spot and anticipate where the others will go becomes crucial. Like zone battle, you need to be focused to fill gaps quickly, but also mindful of the whole field and what\'s happening.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><figure data-embed-type=\"gallery\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220,1300-3767221,1300-3767222,1300-3767223,1300-3767224,1300-3767226,1300-3767227,1300-3767228\" data-resize-urls=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 1rem 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: bold; position: relative; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"image-gallery__label\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(216, 216, 216);\">Gallery</div><div class=\"image-gallery__list hide-scrollbar \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; position: relative; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; display: grid; justify-content: space-between; grid-auto-flow: column; overflow-x: auto;\"><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 1\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767221\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 2\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767222\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 3\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767223\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 4\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767224\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 5\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a></div></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most games, that kind of coordination would require voice chat, but this particular mode benefits from relying on non-verbal communication. It requires more awareness and consideration of your fellow players than the competitive modes because you\'re sharing a single field. The goal of Tetris Effect, across its modes, is to feel the flow of the game without interruption or getting into your own head; silently syncing with your partners, showing them what you plan to do with your next piece and trusting that they\'ll understand and plan around that offers an interesting variation on that theme, and it can create incredible results if you can... connect.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Since it\'s a re-release, we should also talk about what\'s missing from Connected. Unlike the original release, Tetris Effect isn\'t playable in virtual reality. Since Connected is primarily an Xbox release, removing VR seems like a practical decision: The Xbox consoles don\'t support VR headsets, so only PC players would be able to enjoy it. In the original Tetris Effect, VR felt like the coup de gras, tuning you into the game intensely by letting you see and hear the levels all around you. It\'s a unique experience, and part of the magic of the original version. While I think multiplayer is the more approachable feature, and what I would want if forced to choose, I do wish there were a way to have both in a single package.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But there\'s no time for regrets in Tetris. The next piece is falling and you only have a few seconds to put it in place. Then the next piece, and the one after that. Some people meditate to clear their minds. Other people cook, or build models. Tetris Effect has a similar capacity to clear your mind. In 2018, that made Tetris Effect feel special. In 2020, it feels essential.</p>', '2020-12-02', 'djdjdj');
INSERT INTO `games` (`id`, `name`, `rate`, `imagepath`, `author`, `post`, `date`, `itchio_link`) VALUES
(67, 'Game 01', 4, 'http://localhost:8001/uploads/g8-1607043842447.jpg', 'Laura', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In 2018, Tetris Effect\'s mesmerizing sounds and sights heightened the classic game\'s aesthetically pleasing properties and its ability to consume our attention to almost therapeutic levels, reinvigorating our appreciation for one of gaming\'s oldest obsessions. But even as former GameSpot editor Peter Brown proclaimed Tetris \"<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/tetris-effect-review-better-than-ever/1900-6417033/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\"><ins style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px;\">better than ever</ins></a>\" in Tetris Effect, he noted it \"sadly\" did not apply its wondrous approach to multiplayer. Two years later,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gamespot.com/games/tetris-effect-connected/\" data-ref-id=\"5000-516157\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74);\">Tetris Effect: Connected</a>--an updated re-release for Xbox consoles and PC--fills that gap. Just as the original did for the classic version of the game, Connected reimagines Tetris multiplayer with flair and vision. It also loses a major component, VR support, which delivers the most intense version of the experience. While I\'m of two minds on that tradeoff, the soothing intensity of Tetris Effect hasn\'t lost any potency. On the contrary, it feels more vital than ever in 2020.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Though it adds and removes modes whole cloth, the core of Tetris Effect remains unchanged. Despite the fact that Journey mode hasn\'t been touched, its shifting, syncopated themes enraptured me level by level, even on my second time through. Tetris Effect is a significant challenge to average Tetris players like myself. Each level revs the speed up to push you just up to the edge of what you can handle. Even as you improve--and you are getting better, whether you see it or not--the levels scale to demand your full focus. It sounds unapproachable, but there\'s something about the combination of the way your brain looks for patterns, combined with the rhythmic sensory elements and this challenge, that lets you give yourself over to the game, almost trance-like, without even trying.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You\'ll need that focus in multiplayer. Whether you\'re playing cooperatively with other players or competing against them, the multiplayer modes in Connected ratchet up the intensity found in the original. Connected features four multiplayer modes--three competitive, one co-op. As in most games, other players will push you in ways a single-player campaign will not.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767213\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767213-tetriseffectconnected8.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Score Attack in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Most players will rush right to Zone Battle, an updated version of what I imagine when I think of competitive Tetris, a survival mode where completing lines on your field creates extra garbage lines for your opponents. The Connected version adds the zone mechanic from Tetris Effect, which stops the parade of pieces and allows you to complete a large number of lines in a short time. Using zone effectively adds an extra layer of strategy: Activating it at the right time can guarantee a victory, but it\'s surprisingly tricky to find the correct moment to use it. Though it seems like the ability to save up and cash in lines would only intensify the dominance of elite players, I found it allowed you to turn a good flow into a meaningful attack, regardless of whether you\'re winning or losing. It won\'t keep a superior player from stomping you, mind you, but zone rewards players who can be mindful of the situations on both fields and retain the focus to clear lines.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In addition to Zone Battle, Connected also has two versions of Score Attack, a more traditional competitive mode without garbage-line or zone mechanics. In standard Score Attack, you play for the high score and survival. In Classic Score Attack, you do the same, but with the original 1984 rules, so you can\'t bank pieces, use T-Spins, and so on.</p><div class=\"js-mapped-ad mapped-ad mapped-incontent-ad mapped-incontent-ad-dart incontent-leader-loaded\" data-ad-type=\"incontent-ad\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; visibility: visible; position: relative; text-align: center; margin: 1.3rem -100px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"ad-wrap ad-wrap-incontent-ad skybox-inContent\" id=\"incontent-ad\" data-ad=\"incontent-ad\" data-google-query-id=\"CMTImJOQs-0CFQfUGwodgTINow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; line-height: 0;\"><div id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3__container__\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; max-width: none; border: 0pt none; margin: 0px auto !important;\"><iframe id=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" title=\"3rd party ad content\" name=\"google_ads_iframe_/8264/aw-gamespot/gamespace_3\" width=\"728\" height=\"90\" scrolling=\"no\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" frameborder=\"0\" sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" data-google-container-id=\"4\" data-load-complete=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; max-width: none; display: block; vertical-align: bottom; margin: 0px auto !important;\"></iframe></div></div></div><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zone Battle is an interesting riff, but it\'s a known quantity. The most interesting mode--this game\'s crown jewel--is the eponymous Connected co-op mode, where three players collectively try to outlast a series of AI opponents, one at a time. At first, the four players simply play Tetris. The AI enemies, named after the signs of the Zodiac, have special abilities called “blitzes” to make things difficult for you, which range from annoying parlor tricks like moving your field up and down to genuinely infuriating maneuvers like temporarily increasing the speed of your drops to force errors. Once a week, there\'s also an asynchronous Connected Versus mode, where players can spar 3-on-1.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When the three human players clear enough lines on their fields, you automatically trigger a special form of the zone ability, which combines all three of your fields into one. You and your partners take turns placing pieces on the extra-wide field and must clear extra-long lines. Like every level and mode in Tetris Effect, you need to find a natural rhythm in the game, but in this case you do so by getting in sync with your partners. Only one person plays a piece at a time, so being able to quickly find the right spot and anticipate where the others will go becomes crucial. Like zone battle, you need to be focused to fill gaps quickly, but also mindful of the whole field and what\'s happening.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"3840\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 0px -100px 1.3rem; clear: both; text-align: center; max-width: 970px; width: 3840px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"fluid-height\" href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767217\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); max-width: 100%; display: block; position: relative; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; padding-bottom: 546.092px;\"><img alt=\"Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected\" src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png\" srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767217-tetriseffectconnected3.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px\" data-width=\"1280\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 969.991px; height: 546.092px;\"></a><figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; font-family: ArgumentumLightItalic, &quot;Franklin Gothic Medium&quot;, &quot;Arial Narrow Bold&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.48571rem; padding: 0.325rem 20px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: url(&quot;/bundles/gamespotsite/images/bg-border-light.png&quot;); background-position: center bottom; background-repeat: repeat-x;\">Connected mode in Tetris Effect: Connected</figcaption></figure><figure data-embed-type=\"gallery\" data-img-src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220,1300-3767221,1300-3767222,1300-3767223,1300-3767224,1300-3767226,1300-3767227,1300-3767228\" data-resize-urls=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767226-tetriseffectconnected12.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767227-tetriseffectconnected16.png,https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767228-tetriseffectconnected17.png\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin: 1rem 0px; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: bold; position: relative; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div class=\"image-gallery__label\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(216, 216, 216);\">Gallery</div><div class=\"image-gallery__list hide-scrollbar \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; position: relative; padding-top: 1rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; display: grid; justify-content: space-between; grid-auto-flow: column; overflow-x: auto;\"><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767220\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 1\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767220-tetriseffectconnected1.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767221\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 2\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767221-tetriseffectconnected2.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767222\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 3\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767222-tetriseffectconnected6.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767223\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 4\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767223-tetriseffectconnected7.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a><a href=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3767224\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(222, 0, 74); display: block; position: relative; width: 6rem;\"><img src=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/square_avatar/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png\" alt=\"Gallery image 5\" data-full-srcset=\"https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/original/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 3840w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_super/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 1280w, https://gamespot1.cbsistatic.com/uploads/scale_medium/1575/15759911/3767224-tetriseffectconnected11.png 480w\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 95.9971px;\"></a></div></figure><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">In most games, that kind of coordination would require voice chat, but this particular mode benefits from relying on non-verbal communication. It requires more awareness and consideration of your fellow players than the competitive modes because you\'re sharing a single field. The goal of Tetris Effect, across its modes, is to feel the flow of the game without interruption or getting into your own head; silently syncing with your partners, showing them what you plan to do with your next piece and trusting that they\'ll understand and plan around that offers an interesting variation on that theme, and it can create incredible results if you can... connect.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Since it\'s a re-release, we should also talk about what\'s missing from Connected. Unlike the original release, Tetris Effect isn\'t playable in virtual reality. Since Connected is primarily an Xbox release, removing VR seems like a practical decision: The Xbox consoles don\'t support VR headsets, so only PC players would be able to enjoy it. In the original Tetris Effect, VR felt like the coup de gras, tuning you into the game intensely by letting you see and hear the levels all around you. It\'s a unique experience, and part of the magic of the original version. While I think multiplayer is the more approachable feature, and what I would want if forced to choose, I do wish there were a way to have both in a single package.</p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3rem; padding: 0px; font-size: calc(14px + 2 * ((100vw - 320px) / 960)); color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;.SFNSText-Regular&quot;, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;San Francisco&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But there\'s no time for regrets in Tetris. The next piece is falling and you only have a few seconds to put it in place. Then the next piece, and the one after that. Some people meditate to clear their minds. Other people cook, or build models. Tetris Effect has a similar capacity to clear your mind. In 2018, that made Tetris Effect feel special. In 2020, it feels essential.</p>', '2020-12-23', 'dddd'),
(70, 'delete', 1, 'http://localhost:8001/uploads/overland-1607082844802.png', '1', '<div class=\"post-header\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"cat\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://nochgames.com/category/gaming-blog-series/\" rel=\"category tag\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 3px 7px 4px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background: rgb(239, 52, 24); text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 1px;\">GAMING BLOG SERIES</a></span><span class=\"comment-box\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 3px 6px; float: right; background-color: rgb(187, 187, 187); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline-block; position: relative; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px;\"><a href=\"https://nochgames.com/how-to-start-a-gaming-blog/#comments\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">11</a></span><h1 class=\"entry-title\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; font-family: Oswald; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 38px;\">How To Start A Gaming Blog Today (Step by step)</h1><div class=\"post-meta\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://nochgames.com/2017/06/27/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">On Jun 27, 2017 11:49 pm</a>, by&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nochgames.com/author/amieee/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">Amie Botes</a></span></div></div><div data-direction=\"ltr\" class=\"post-image\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img width=\"700\" height=\"485\" src=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Blog-Features-3-min.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" alt=\"how to start a gaming blog\" srcset=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Blog-Features-3-min.jpg 700w, https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Blog-Features-3-min-650x450.jpg 650w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></div><div class=\"post-entry\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-1630 alignright\" src=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Gaming-Content-min.jpg\" alt=\"how to start a gaming blog\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline; float: right;\">How to start a gaming blog and become a video game blogger – The Ultimate Guide!</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Have you ever tried to start a gaming blog before, writing a gazillion articles, trying to stay up to date with all the gaming news and at the end of the day when you go to Google Analytics you see only traces of your own visits?</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Don’t feel bad!!!</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">It’s happening to a lot of people out there believe me, because I was also one of&nbsp;</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">them! It’s the fastest way reality slap you in the face and you give up because you start to think it’s impossible.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">How can no one like my awesome blog and fail so spectacularly?</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The problem is that it’s easy to start a gaming blog, buying a domain, create a website that looks cool, write a few articles to start off with and promote it on your social media accounts.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Although all of that is definitely important, I will cover it later in the post.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The hard part is to actually create high quality content and keep it going consistently, building an audience/readership and establishing your blog’s brand.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">So I went to Google and searched…. And searched …. And searched, but there were no real article or blog that could explain in detail how to start a gaming blog that would actually work.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The only results that come up in Google when you search “how to create a gaming blog” is explaining the process in a very broad sense without any details on how actually to create your gaming blog.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">So I decided to dedicate my time to create the most comprehensive Series on how to start a gaming blog from scratch, step by step.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">This post is only Part 1 of 6, here is the whole&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nochgames.com/category/gaming-blog-series/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(239, 52, 24);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Gaming Blog Series</strong></a>.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-426 size-full\" src=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Grow-Your-Audience.jpg\" alt=\"how To Start A Gaming Blog From Scratch - nochgames.com\" width=\"900\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Grow-Your-Audience.jpg 900w, https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Grow-Your-Audience-300x200.jpg 300w, https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Grow-Your-Audience-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block;\"></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Every one of us, you included, have somewhere dive into something head first and thought it would be awesome and easy.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">From hearing success stories and watching motivational videos we get so psyched up that we never really take the time to plan a proper strategy.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">By all means dream big, because anyone is capable of succeeding in creating an awesome gaming blog, you’ll see.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">But before we start, here are 4 important questions you should ask yourself and I advise that you have a clear answer these questions before you read further.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">#1 Asking Yourself The Right Questions Before You Start</b></h2><hr style=\"margin-top: 0px; padding: 0px; border-top: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); clear: both;\"><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Question 1 – Why do you want to start a gaming blog?</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Is gaming really my passion and do I really want to learn more about the topic. Well the answer is you should love it, otherwise it’s not going to work out.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Your “why” should be the reason you will keep going, even when you don’t feel like keep trying.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">This is critical because blogging is a lot of writing, research and it will get tough at times when you desperately need new ideas. The most important way to keep motivated is to consistently create high quality content for your audience.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">This will be very satisfying once you start and learn more with time.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Question 2 – What is your main goal for starting a gaming blog, what do want to achieve?</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Without a clear goal, it’s almost certain that it is going to fail. So write it down and think about it for a second.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">The more specific, the better. Start small, but be specific.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">For example here is mine: “I want to help a 100 people start their gaming blog in 2017.”</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-428 size-full\" src=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Smart-Goals.jpg\" alt=\"how To Start A Gaming Blog From Scratch - nochgames.com\" width=\"800\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Smart-Goals.jpg 800w, https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Smart-Goals-300x131.jpg 300w, https://nochgames.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/Smart-Goals-768x336.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block;\"></p><h3 style=\"margin-bottom: 20px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-size: 21px; font-family: Oswald, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">Question 3 – Is there enough people out there who will read my blog?</strong></h3><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Well definitely! You just have to find your audience and give them what they want, not what you think they want. It is often one of the main reasons why blogs in any niche fails.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">It will also depend on the sub-topics you choose to write about and how you promote your content to your audience.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">&nbsp;</p></div>', '2020-12-31', '1');
